PortSystem 1.0

name	   tcl-tls
version	   1.5.0
categories	devel
platforms	darwin
maintainers	jmpp@opendarwin.org

description	TLS OpenSSL extension to TCL.
long_description	TLS is an OpenSSL / RSA-bsafe Tcl extension that provides secure \
			connections on top of the Tcl socket mechanism.

